  "text": "Deformation was then measured using the ATOS system as described previously. [CITATION_1] To summarise the method, each shell was measured pre-and postimplantation and the scans compared to determine the magnitude of the deformation at a plane 1.5 mm below the rim. The data evaluation method slightly differed to that utilised previously, [CITATION_2] where the difference in the maximum inscribed circle was compared.",
